    <h3 align=center id=qname>Polar Bear Cloak</h3><hr size=1>
	 <table width=100% cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 border=0>
	 <tr><td valign=top>
	 <table cellpadding=1 cellspacing=1 border=0 align=left>
	 <tr><td><b>Starts in:</b></td><td><a href='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Everfrost.htm'>Everfrost Peaks</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Who:</b></td><td><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=3611>Karg Icebear</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Rating:</b></td><td>Average (3.87)</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Estimated Time:</b></td><td>1 hour</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Minimum Level:</b></td><td>6</td></tr><tr><td><b>Best Class:</b></td><td>All</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Quest Items:</b></span><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=3044">Polar Bear Hide</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Related Creatures:</b></span><li><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=645>A Polar Bear</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td id=rt><b>Submitted by:</b></td><td>Doriath and Beonar</td></tr></td></tr></table>Karg Icebear wanders the tundra, often passing by the North Tower.  He will make a Polar Bear Cloak for A polar bear skin (cannot be ruined) and 5 pp.</td></tr>
